    "})\n",
    "print(f\"[XGBoost] F1-Weighted: {xgb_f1_weighted:.4f} | F1-Macro: {xgb_f1_macro:.4f} | Balanced Acc: {xgb_balanced_acc:.4f} | ROC-AUC: {xgb_roc_auc:.4f}\")\n",
